text: Ositie ebuleka owawenya mubo, ne obukule owawenya. Ne niwenya ulia owawara elubeka, shinobubii khubo tawe. Okhukhola endio khwitsa okhuchila tsimoni tsiabu tsisangale, nebalabeelela tawe, ne babe nobuchami khushilia shiobahelesia, abo boosi. Ne Nyasaye amanyile kali mumioyo chienyu, ne Nyasaye ni Omumanyi(omuholo) Omwihotselefu
